{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t4-train-3","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数","title":"针对训练3：绝对值最值问题","difficulty":4,"tags":["绝对值","最值"],"content":"若 $|a - 3| + |b + 2| = 0$，求 $a + b$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"利用绝对值非负性","content":"因为 $|a - 3| \\geq 0$，$|b + 2| \\geq 0$\n\n且 $|a - 3| + |b + 2| = 0$\n\n所以 $|a - 3| = 0$ 且 $|b + 2| = 0$","formula":"a = 3 \\text{，} b = -2"},{"title":"求和","content":"$a + b = 3 + (-2) = 1$","formula":"a + b = 1"}]},"id":"t4-train-3"},"__N_SSG":true}